main#content.bs-docs-masthead(role='main', tabindex='-1')
	.container
		span.bs-docs-booticon.bs-docs-booticon-lg.bs-docs-booticon-outline B
		p.lead
			| Bootstrap is the most popular HTML, CSS, and JS framework for developing responsive, mobile first projects on the web.
		p.lead
			a.btn.btn-outline-inverse.btn-lg(href='getting-started#download', onclick="ga('send', 'event', 'Jumbotron actions', 'Download', 'Download {{ site.current_version }}');") Download Bootstrap
		p.version Currently v{{ site.current_version }}
		| {% include ads.html %}
.bs-docs-featurette
	.container
		h2.bs-docs-featurette-title Designed for everyone, everywhere.
		p.lead
			| Bootstrap makes front-end web development faster and easier. It's made for folks of all skill levels, devices of all shapes, and projects of all sizes.
		hr.half-rule
		.row
			.col-sm-4
				img.img-responsive(src='assets/img/sass-less.png', alt='Sass and Less support')
				h3 Preprocessors
				p
					| Bootstrap ships with vanilla CSS, but its source code utilizes the two most popular CSS preprocessors, 
					a(href='../css/#less') Less
					|  and 
					a(href='../css/#sass') Sass
					| . Quickly get started with precompiled CSS or build on the source.
			.col-sm-4
				img.img-responsive(src='assets/img/devices.png', alt='Responsive across devices')
				h3 One framework, every device.
				p
					| Bootstrap easily and efficiently scales your websites and applications with a single code base, from phones to tablets to desktops with CSS media queries.
			.col-sm-4
				img.img-responsive(src='assets/img/components.png', alt='Components')
				h3 Full of features
				p
					| With Bootstrap, you get extensive and beautiful documentation for common HTML elements, dozens of custom HTML and CSS components, and awesome jQuery plugins.
		hr.half-rule
		p.lead Bootstrap is open source. It's hosted, developed, and maintained on GitHub.
		a.btn.btn-outline.btn-lg(href='{{ site.repo }}') View the GitHub project
.bs-docs-featurette
	.container
		h2.bs-docs-featurette-title Built with Bootstrap.
		p.lead
			| Millions of amazing sites across the web are being built with Bootstrap. Get started on your own with our growing 
			a(href='../getting-started/#examples') collection of examples
			|  or by exploring some of our favorites.
		hr.half-rule
		.row.bs-docs-featured-sites
			| {% for showcase in site.data.showcase %}
			.col-xs-6.col-sm-3
				a(href='{{ showcase.expo_url }}', target='_blank', title='{{ showcase.name }}')
					img.img-responsive(src='{{ site.baseurl }}/assets/img/expo-{{ showcase.img }}.jpg', alt='{{ showcase.name }}')
			| {% endfor %}
		hr.half-rule
		p.lead
			| We showcase dozens of inspiring projects built with Bootstrap on the Bootstrap Expo.
		a.btn.btn-outline.btn-lg(href='{{ site.expo }}') Explore the Expo
